th%20AndrenaM%2C%20a%20startup%20using%20artificial%20intelligence%20to%20analyze%20sonar%20data%20and%20deliver%20real-time%20insights%2C%20this%20legacy%20defense%20tool%20is%20finally%20getting%20a%20high-tech%20upgrade.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20vision%20is%20to%20secure%20the%20oceans%2C%26quot%3B%20Matej%20Cernosek%2C%20AndrenaM%20cofounder%20and%20CEO%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20an%20interview.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20doing%20that%20by%20building%20a%20distributed%20sensing%20network%20%E2%80%94%20a%20sonar%20mesh.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAndrenaM's%20%2410%20million%20seed%20round%20closed%20in%2036%20hours.%20Typically%2C%20this%20process%20takes%20early-stage%20startups%20weeks%2C%20even%20months.%20Its%20rapid%20fundraise%20signals%20just%20how%20eager%20investors%20are%20about%20the%20new%20wave%20of%20defense%20tech.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFirst%20Round%20Capital%20led%20the%20fundraise%2C%20with%20participation%20from%20Also%20Capital%2C%20Long%20Journey%2C%20Homebrew%2C%20and%20the%20Colorado%20School%20of%20Mines%20Venture%20Fund%2C%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202024%2C%20Cernosek%2C%20a%20former%20SpaceX%20engineer%2C%20started%20the%20Hawthorne%2C%20Calif.-based%20company%20with%20cofounder%20and%20Chief%20Technology%20Officer%20Alex%20Chu.%20The%20two%20met%20during%20their%20first%20week%20of%20college%20at%20the%20Colorado%20School%20of%20Mines%2C%20where%20they%20both%20studied%20mechanical%20engineering.%20Chu%20previously%20worked%20at%20a%20robotics%20company%20and%20as%20a%20software%20engineer%20at%20Qualia%2C%20a%20real%20estate%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20decades%20of%20sonar%20use%2C%20much%20of%20the%20data%20processing%20is%20still%20manual%20and%20analog.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20been%20people%20in%20these%20shacks%20that%20have%20headphones%20on%2C%20looking%20at%20a%20fuzzy%20screen%20and%20analyzing%20data%20coming%20to%20them%20in%20mass%2C%26quot%3B%20Cernosek%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAndrenaM's%20eight-person