%3E%2C%20in%20partnership%20with%20Microsoft%20and%20Nvidia-backed%20self-driving%20startup%20Wayve.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20two%20companies%20prepare%20to%20launch%20their%20robotaxi%20service%2C%20I%20took%20a%20test%20drive%20through%20the%20busy%20streets%20of%20central%20London%20in%20one%20of%20the%20self-driving%20Ford%20Mach-Es%20Wayve%20has%20been%20testing%20in%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20robotaxi%20dealt%20with%20everything%20London's%20chaotic%20driving%20environment%20could%20throw%20at%20it%2C%20with%20Wayve%20CEO%20Alex%20Kendall%2C%20who%20joined%20for%20the%20ride%2C%20saying%20it%20was%20one%20of%20the%20more%20eventful%20trips%20he'd%20taken.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2247282123-1b1f-42f9-bc79-3dc00cd2a6b3%5C%22%3ERobot%2C%20take%20the%20wheel%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20quick%20look%20around%20Wayve's%20Kings%20Cross%20base%2C%20we%20hopped%20in%20a%20Ford%20Mach-E%20equipped%20with%20the%20company's%20%26quot%3BAI%20driver%26quot%3B%20self-driving%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWayve's%20upcoming%20robotaxi%20service%20with%20Uber%20will%20be%20fully%20driverless%2C%20but%20for%20now%2C%20the%20company%20is%20testing%20with%20safety%20drivers%20who%20take%20over%20if%20the%20robotaxi%20runs%20into%20problems.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Wayve%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F684ad5b33d5881a51c1b4544%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWayve's%20robotaxi%20out%20and%20about%20in%20central%20London.%3Cp%3EWayve%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20sat%20in%20the%20front%20seat%2C%20alongside%20a%20big%20red%20button%20that%20disengages%20the%20self-driving%20system%20(the%20safety%20driver%20on%20my%20ride%20said%20he'd%20never%20had%20to%20use%20it).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20driver%20drove%20us%20out%20of%20the%20gates%20of%20Wayve's%20HQ%20and%20then%2C%20with%20a%20sharp%20buzzing%20noise%2C%20he%20removed%20his%20hands%20from%20the%20wheel%2C%20and%20the%20robotaxi%20took%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELondon's%20streets%20are%20famously%20complex%2C%20so%20much%20so%20that%20taxi%20drivers%20are%20required%20to%20learn%20thousands%20of%20them%20off%20by%20heart%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-artificial-intelligence-impact-on-companies-pay-office-workers-uber-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ea%20150-year-old%20exam%20known%20as%20%26quot%3BThe%20Knowledge.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20city's%20hodgepodge%20of%20Roman%20and%20Victorian%20roads%20are%20a%20mess%20of%20cycle%20lanes%20and%20pedestrian%20crossings%2C%20with%20complex%20road%20layouts%20that%20often%20serve%20more%20as%20a%20rough%20guide%20than%20a%20rulebook%20for%20the%20millions%20of%20drivers%20passing%20through%20the%20city%20each%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Wayve%2C%20that%20complexity%20is%20the%20point.%20The%20company%20says%20its%20AI%20driver%20%E2%80%94%20which%20runs%20on%20an%20end-to-end%20AI%20model%2C%20an%20approach%20also%20adopted%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-prioritizes-musk-vip-data-self-driving-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETesla%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20is%20capable%20of%20generalizing%20and%20reacting%20to%20the%20physical%20world%20in%20the%20same%20way%20a%20human%20would%2C%20unlike%20rivals%20like%20Waymo%2C%20which%20rely%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwaymo-early-talks-toyota-partnership-autonomous-driving-personally-owned-cars-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehigh-definition%20maps%20and%20sensors%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKendall%20said%20that%20this%20allows%20Wayve's%20software%20to%20drive%20anywhere%2C%20even%20places%20it%20hasn't%20seen%20before%2C%20and%20deal%20with%20the%20kind%20of%20unexpected%20encounters%20that%20are%20an%20everyday%20occurrence%20on%20the%20streets%20of%20a%20major%20city%20like%20London.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20can't%20wait%20to%20see%20another%20autonomy%20company%20come%20into%20London%20because%20I%20think%20it's%20extremely%20challenging%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Kendall.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20advantage%20of%20starting%20in%20London%20is%20that%20we've%20been%20forced%20to%20develop%20a%20system%20that%20can%20operate%20on%20complex%20roads%20and%20deal%20with%20all%20of%20these%20unexpected%20scenarios%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229264b768-e259-4071-9ba3-c575716e5c8d%5C%22%3EOn%20the%20road%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20first%20few%20minutes%20of%20our%20drive%2C%20we%20encountered%20multiple%20jaywalkers%2C%20including%20several%20who%20darted%20out%20across%20the%20street%20without%20warning%20in%20front%20of%20the%20robotaxi.%20We%20also%20had%20to%20inch%20through%20narrow%20gaps%20between%20rows%20of%20parked%20cars.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPerhaps%20understandably%2C%20Wayve's%20robotaxi%20was%20more%20cautious%20than%20your%20average%20Uber%20driver.%20On%20one%20occasion%2C%20the%20robotaxi%20came%20to%20a%20jerky%20stop%20at%20an%20amber%20light%20when%20it%20may%20have%20had%20enough%20time%20to%20go%20through.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Wayve%20Warwick%204x%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.jwplayer.com%2Fplayers%2FfaSDpHte-puACk8ZV.html%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3ESometimes%2C%20that%20caution%20was%20too%20much%20for%20London's%20impatient%20commuters.%20One%20maneuver%20that%20saw%20the%20car%20slowly%20navigate%20a%20tight%20gap%20between%20a%20set%20of%20roadworks%20and%20a%20row%20of%20traffic%20drew%20an%20irate%20honk%20from%20the%20car%20behind%2C%20which%20was%20clearly%20keen%20for%20us%20to%20hurry%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWayve%20has%20been%20testing%20its%20autonomous%20vehicles%20on%20the%20streets%20of%20London%20for%20years%2C%20but%20they%20still%20run%20into%20the%20odd%20surprise.%20Around%20halfway%20into%20our%20drive%2C%20we%20came%20across%20a%20roadblock%20as%20a%20team%20of%20workers%20trimmed%20an%20overhanging%20tree.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20seat%20behind%20me%2C%20Kendall%20broke%20off%20from%20answering%20my%20question%20and%20leaned%20forward%20to%20see%20how%20the%20car%20would%20deal%20with%20the%20falling%20branches%20and%20the%20worker%20directing%20traffic%20%E2%80%94%20but%20the%20robotaxi%20barely%20paused%2C%20successfully%20reading%20hand%20signals%20to%20stop%20and%20proceed%20and%20accelerating%20past%20the%20quizzical%20stares%20of%20the%20maintenance%20crew.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20never%20seen%20that%20before%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Kendall%20as%20the%20robotaxi%20exited%20the%20roadblock%2C%20also%20dodging%20a%20tractor%20reversing%20along%20the%20road.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20route%20skirted%20the%20edge%20of%20Soho%2C%20London's%20central%20nightlife%20district%2C%20and%20went%20past%20the%20entrance%20to%20the%20British%20Museum%2C%20a%20narrow%20street%20packed%20with%20tourists%2C%20taxi%20drivers%2C%20and%20roadworks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPerhaps%20the%20most%20impressive%20moment%20of%20the%20drive%20came%20on%20this%20road%2C%20one%20of%20London's%20busiest.%20The%20robotaxi%20came%20to%20a%20stop%20at%20a%20crosswalk%20in%20near%20constant%20use%20as%20a%20huge%20crowd%20of%20pedestrians%20streamed%20toward%20the%20Museum.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWorking%20out%20the%20safe%20moment%20to%20move%20forward%20would%20be%20daunting%20even%20for%20a%20human%20driver%2C%20but%20the%20car%20spotted%20an%20opening%20and%20moved%20through%20the%20zebra%20crossing%20quickly%2C%20avoiding%20traffic%20building%20up%20behind%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLots%20of%20autonomy%20systems%2C%20I%20think%2C%20would%20be%20stuck%20here%20for%20hours%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Kendall%2C%20explaining%20that%20moments%20like%20this%20required%20the%20robotaxi's%20AI%20software%20to%20track%20and%20predict%20the%20activity%20of%20dozens%20of%20pedestrians.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e0db9b62-c758-4917-8c97-a4f497f9e047%5C%22%3EA%20glimpse%20into%20the%20future%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20drive%20went%20on%2C%20the%20activity%20around%20us%20occasionally%20passed%20into%20the%20bizarre.%20While%20coming%20to%20a%20stop%20at%20a%20red%20light%2C%20we%20narrowly%20avoided%20being%20hit%20by%20a%20small%20piece%20of%20metal%20that%20fell%20off%20the%20truck%20in%20front%20as%20it%20accelerated%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20pedestrian%20crossing%20at%20the%20red%20light%20kindly%20picked%20up%20the%20debris%20and%20moved%20it%20to%20the%20side%20of%20the%20road%2C%20but%20it's%20hard%20to%20imagine%20anyone%20thinking%20to%20simulate%20a%20situation%20so%20surreal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Kendall%2C%20incidents%20like%20this%20are%20proof%20that%20robotaxis%20need%20to%20get%20on%20as%20many%20roads%20as%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Wayve%20Varese%204x%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.jwplayer.com%2Fplayers%2F4hAvQq8e-puACk8ZV.html%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20opening%20offices%20in%20Canada%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwayve-ceo-testing-driverless-cars-us-expansion-ai-robotics-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethe%20US%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20Japan%20over%20the%20last%20year%2C%20Wayve%20has%20now%20tested%20its%20vehicles%20in%2090%20cities%20in%20the%20past%2090%20days%2C%20from%20alpine%20roads%20in%20Switzerland%20and%20dirt%20tracks%20in%20rural%20Italy%20to%20bustling%20cities%20like%20Tokyo%20and%20Vancouver.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKendall%20said%20for%20some%20of%20those%20places%2C%20Wayve%20had%20little%20to%20no%20training%20data%2C%20demonstrating%20the%20ability%20of%20its%20software%20to%20apply%20what%20it%20has%20learnt%20to%20completely%20new%20cities%20and%20driving%20environments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20robotaxis%20are%20just%20going%20to%20be%20in%20affluent%20areas%20like%20the%20Bay%20Area%2C%20then%20we've%20failed%20as%20an%20industry.%20We've%20got%20to%20make%20sure%20this%20technology%20is%20rolled%20out%20globally%2C%26quot%3B%20Kendall%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20launch%20of%20a%20driverless%20ride-hailing%20service%20with%20Uber%20in%20London%2C%20which%20will%20be%20the%20first%20time%20Wayve%20has%20taken%20the%20safety%20driver%20out%20of%20its%20vehicles%2C%20is%20a%20big%20step%20toward%20that%20vision.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Wayve%20Chiyoda%204X%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.jwplayer.com%2Fplayers%2FShkf4bpv-puACk8ZV.html%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20companies%20declined%20to%20say%20when%20the%20driverless%20pilots%20would%20begin%20or%20which%20automaker%20would%20supply%20the%20vehicles%20for%20the%20robotaxi%20fleet%2C%20but%20Kendall%20described%20it%20as%20a%20huge%20moment%20for%20the%20young%20British%20startup%20and%20the%20broader%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20exciting%2C%20it's%20my%20life's%20work.%20Over%2099%25%20of%20road%20accidents%20are%20due%20to%20human%20error%2C%20and%20this%20technology%20can%20eliminate%20those%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225e39761a-a9b2-4484-ba73-4b74e8e0f04b%5C%22%3EA%20long%20road%20ahead%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20ride%20in%20Wayve's%20robotaxi%20ended%20with%20the%20car%20smoothly%20negotiating%20a%20doub