p%3EMany%20of%20the%20key%20points%20of%20a%20performance%20review%2C%C2%A0such%20as%20how%20your%20work%20connects%20to%20an%20OKR%20or%20other%20performance%20metric%2C%C2%A0can%20become%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20updates%20to%20show%20your%20continuing%20contributions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20other%20factors%20to%20consider%20include%20reviews%20from%20collaborators%2C%20your%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmistakes-managers-make-during-performance-reviews-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emanager's%20assessment%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20your%20performance%20relative%20to%20your%20peers%2C%20and%20how%20your%20work%20helped%20the%20company's%20overall%20performance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2279de9d6d-a2a7-4462-b44c-4d1436f30d85%5C%22%3EKeeping%20your%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20updated%20could%20help%20during%20a%20layoff%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20if%20your%20performance%20and%20your%20ratings%20are%20solid%2C%20there's%20a%20possibility%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frecent-company-layoffs-laying-off-workers-2025%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehead%20count%20reduction%3C%2Fa%3E%20if%20the%20company%20doesn't%20meet%20investor%20or%20shareholder%20expectations%2C%26quot%3B%20Phadk%C3%A9%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20may%20choose%20to%20look%20for%20another%20role%2C%20or%20you%20may%20not%20have%20a%20choice.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWaiting%20until%20you%20need%20your%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20revamped%2C%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-layoffs-employees-laid-off-advice-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eafter%20a%20layoff%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20can%20create%20a%20stressful%2C%20panicked%20situation%20as%20you%20hunt%20through%20documentation%20under%20the%20gun%20of%20job-search%20deadline%20pressures.%20By%20making%20it%20routine%20to%20update%20your%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20after%20every%20performance%20review%2C%20you'll%20be%20ahead%20of