ETo%20date%2C%20healthcare%20PE%20has%20largely%20been%20marked%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerican-hospitals-bankrupt-closing-wealthy-investors-looting-reselling-private-equity-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efirms%20buying%20and%20combining%20in-person%20physician%20practices%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20everything%20from%20hospitals%20to%20dentists'%20offices%20to%20medspas.%20Holt%20has%20eschewed%20physician%20group%20rollups%20to%20dig%20deep%20into%20healthtech%20instead%2C%20with%20numerous%20megadeals%20behind%20his%20thesis%2C%20from%20New%20Mountain's%20%247%20billion%20merger%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-unicorn-datavant-looking-for-healthcare-acquisition-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EDatavant%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Ciox%20Health%20in%202021%20to%20its%20%245%20billion%20healthcare%20payments%20rollup%20of%20Machinify%2C%20The%20Rawlings%20Group%2C%20Apixio%2C%20and%20Varis%20in%20January.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20Holt%20isn't%20afraid%20to%20pay%20up%20for%20a%20fast-growing%20asset.%20For%20its%20Smarter%20Technologies%20rollup%2C%20New%20Mountain%20paid%20around%20%241%20billion%20in%20cash%20and%20stock%20just%20to%20acquire%20SmarterDx%2C%20multiple%20people%20with%20knowledge%20of%20the%20deal%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20been%20a%20rough%20few%20years%20for%20healthcare%20private%20markets%2C%20with%20only%20a%20handful%20of%20IPOs%20and%20few%20acquisitions%2C%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstakes-for-healthcare-ipo-are-higher-than-ever-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epublic%20healthcare%20companies%20tumble%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20buyers%20in%20Big%20Tech%20and%20health%20insurance%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbig-healthcare-startup-buyers-gone-acquisition-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etake%20a%20step%20back%20from%20healthtech%20M%26amp%3BA%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20made%20l