n%3ENew%20Mountain's%20Smarter%20Technologies%20combines%20Access%20Healthcare%2C%20SmarterDx%2C%20and%20Thoughtful%20AI%20into%20a%20health%20AI%20giant%20to%20compete%20in%20hospital%20revenue%20cycle%20management.%3Cp%3ENew%20Mountain%20Capital%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228039e466-664d-4730-b037-fd8e2981d00b%5C%22%3EPrivate%20equity%20meets%20venture%20studio%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMultiple%20investors%20and%20bankers%20told%20BI%20that%20New%20Mountain's%20healthcare%20returns%20are%20impressive.%20While%20those%20returns%20aren't%20public%2C%20Holt%20has%20led%20some%20of%20the%20biggest%20healthcare%20deals%20of%20the%20last%20few%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcvs-home-healthcare-signify-health-deal-2022-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESignify%20Health%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20created%20inside%20New%20Mountain%20in%202017%2C%20saw%20one%20such%20blockbuster%20deal%3B%20the%20home%20healthtech%20company%20went%20public%20in%202021%20and%20was%20acquired%20in%202023%20by%20CVS%20Health%20for%20%248%20billion.%20In%20the%20biopharma%20and%20medtech%20category%2C%20New%20Mountain%20sold%20manufacturing%20company%20ILC%20Dover%20to%20Ingersoll%20Rand%20in%202024%20for%20%242.3%20billion.%20A%20few%20years%20back%2C%20in%202019%2C%20the%20firm%20saw%20its%20life%20sciences%20tools%20company%20Avantor%20go%20public%20at%20over%20a%20%2414%20billion%20valuation%2C%20and%20sold%20health%20payments%20company%20Equian%20to%20UnitedHealth%20Group's%20Optum%20for%20%243.2%20billion%20the%20same%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20returns%20have%20given%20Holt%20further%20license%20to%20deviate%20from%20PE%20tradition.%20By%20his%20own%20admission%2C%20he's%20adopted%20a%20model%20for%20building%20companies%20that's%20part%20PE%2C%20part%20venture%20studio.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20identify%20a%20problem%20statement%20in%20the%20industry%2C%20and%20then%20we%20put%20a%20blueprint%20together%20of%20what%20would%20be%20the%20company%20that%20we%20would%20build%20to%20best%20go%20after%20that%20problem%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20what%20we're%20really%20doing%20is%20we're%20taking%20a%20page%20out%20of%20the%20venture%20studio%20playbook%20and%20applying%20the%20same%20process%2C%20but%20with%20the%20advantage%20of%20starting%20with%20a%20large-scale%20private%20equity%20fund.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20many%20private%20equity%20firms%2C%20New%20Mountain%20uses%20its%20funds%20to%20buy%20or%20build%20a%20stable%20underlying%20business%20and%20then%20acquire%20additional%20companies%20to%20achieve%20scale.%20Unlike%20most%20private%20equity%20funds%2C%20profitability%20isn't%20the%20main%20focus%20of%20getting%20that%20scale%2C%20at%20least%20not%20at%20first.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAggregating%20different%20pieces%20like%20they've%20done%20with%20%5BSmarter%20Technologies%5D%20isn't%20unusual.%20Private%20equity%20rollups%20are%20the%20first%2010%20pages%20of%20the%20playbook%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Bryan%20Roberts%2C%20a%20partner%20at%20Venrock.%20%26quot%3BApplying%20technology%20and%20data%2C%20and%20going%20for%20growth%20rather%20than%20just%20EBITDA%2C%20is%20the%20interesting%20twist.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Smarter%20Technologies%20team%2C%20including%20CEO%20Jeremy%20Delinsky.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F684b2dd43d5881a51c1b5148%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Smarter%20Technologies%20team%2C%20including%20CEO%20Jeremy%20Delinsky.%3Cp%3ESmarter%20Technologies%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20twist%20has%20led%20Holt%20to%20buy%20several%20younger%2C%20venture-backed%20startups%2C%20a%20rare%20feat%20for%20PE%2C%20since%20venture-backed%20startups%20often%20focus%20more%20on%20achieving%20blockbuster%20growth%20than%20profitability.%20SmarterDx%20last%20raised%20a%20%2450%20million%20Series%20B%20funding%20round%20in%20May%202024%2C%20while%20Thoughtful%20AI%20last%20raised%20a%20%2420%20million%20Series%20A%20in%20July.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20PE%20deals%20often%20take%20the%20form%20of%20leveraged%20buyouts%2C%20wherein%20a%20firm%20invests%20borrowed%20money%20with%20the%20company's%20assets%20as%20collateral%2C%20New%20Mountain%20can't%20and%20doesn't%20fund%20those%20startup%20deals%20with%20debt%2C%20since%20startups%20don't%20usually%20have%20the%20stable%20cash%20flows%20or%20other%20assets%20to%20derisk%20the%20loans.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20LBO-light%20approach%20is%20part%20of%20New%20Mountain's%20strategy%20in%20every%20sector%2C%20not%20just%20healthcare%20%E2%80%94%20New%20Mountain's%20website%20says%20the%20firm%20%26quot%3Bemphasizes%20business%20building%20and%20growth%2C%20rather%20than%20debt%2C%20as%20it%20pursues%20long-term%20capital%20appreciation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20performance%20of%20New%20Mountain's%20previous%20healthcare%20bets%20has%20also%20given%20the%20firm%20freedom%20to%20hold%20onto%20assets%20past%20when%20they'd%20generally%20be%20expected%20to%20generate%20a%20return%2C%20usually%20within%20a%20ten-year%20period.%20Holt%20said%20he's%20rolled%20several%20of%20New%20Mountain's%20largest%20healthcare%20investments%2C%20including%20Datavant%2C%20Swoop%2C%20and%20Real%20Chemistry%2C%20into%20continuation%20funds%20to%20allow%20them%20to%20continue%20growing%20without%20strict%20time%20constraints.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20returns%20may%20be%20around%20the%20corner%2C%20though%2C%20as%20at%20least%20one%20of%20New%20Mountain's%20portfolio%20companies%20looks%20to%20be%20preparing%20for%20an%20IPO.%20Datavant%20CEO%20Kyle%20Armbrester%20told%20BI%20in%20January%20that%20he%20expected%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-unicorn-datavant-looking-for-healthcare-acquisition-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emake%20multiple%20healthcare%20acquisitions%20this%20year%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20rounding%20out%20the%20company%20with%20more%20features%20and%20revenue%20in%20a%20strategy%20that%20could%20make%20it%20more%20attractive%20for%20a%20public%20market%20debut.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20certainly%20at%20a%20size%20and%20scale%20where%20going%20public%20could%20be%20something%20that%20we%20contemplate%2C%26quot%3B%20Armbrester%20said%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222832%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kyle%20Armbrester%2C%20CEO%20of%20Datavant.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F684b2ceb3d5881a51c1b5124%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222124%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKyle%20Armbrester%2C%20CEO%20of%20Datavant.%3Cp%3EDatavant%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d60d894b-c8fd-4083-ab17-580e0e8ef5d7%5C%22%3EHealthcare%20PE's%20rocky%20reputation%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Venn%20diagram%20of%20private%20equity%20and%20venture%20capital%2C%20more%20firms%20on%20both%20sides%20are%20making%20bets%20in%20the%20center.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVC%20firms%2C%20including%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgeneral-catalyst-hemant-taneja-redefine-venture-capital-baffling-industry-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGeneral%20Catalyst%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%20Thrive%20Capital%2C%20are%20buying%20up%20accounting%20firms%20and%20other%20businesses%20in%20PE-like%20rollups%20that%20rely%20on%20AI%20to%20make%20the%20combined%20companies%20more%20efficient.%20And%2C%20as%20venture-backed%20startups%20desperate%20for%20an%20exit%20face%20a%20volatile%20IPO%20market%20and%20antitrust%20concerns%20from%20Big%20Tech%20buyers%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmore-startups-get-bought-up-by-private-equity-vc-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPE%20firms%20from%20KKR%20to%20Thoma%20Bravo%20are%20scooping%20them%20up%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20healthcare%2C%20most%20PE%20investment%20still%20goes%20toward%20care%20delivery%20companies.%20But%20New%20Mountain%20isn't%20the%20only%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbig-deals-coming-healthcare-startups-take-privates-private-equity-2024%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPE%20firm%20interested%20in%20new%20health%20technologies%3C%2Fa%3E.%20TowerBrook%20Capital%20and%20CD%26amp%3BR%20bought%20AI-powered%20revenue%20cycle%20management%20company%20R1%20RCM%20last%20year%20for%20%248.9%20billion.%20In%20March%2C%20Clearlake%20Capital%20bought%20a%20majority%20stake%20in%20ModMed%2C%20an%20electronic%20health%20records%20and%20health%20AI%20software%20maker%2C%20in%20a%20deal%20valuing%20the%20company%20at%20%245.3%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPrivate%20equity's%20rising%20interest%20in%20healthtech%20means%20more%20competition%20for%20New%20Mountain%20and%20Holt.%20New%20Mountain%20bid%20on%20then-public%20R1%20RCM%20itself%20in%20early%202024%2C%20before%20TowerBrook%20and%20CD%26amp%3BR's%20buyout.%20The%20firm%20took%20a%2032%25%20stake%20in%20R1%20RCM%20in%202022%20after%20investing%20%24400%20million%20in%20revenue%20cycle%20tech%20company%20CloudMed%20and%20selling%20it%20to%20R1%20RCM%20for%20%244.1%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHolt%20said%20the%20firm%20sold%20its%20full%20stake%20in%20R1%20RCM%20as%20part%20of%20the%20buyout%20at%20a%20%26quot%3Bsignificant%20premium.%26quot%3B%20Then%2C%20New%20Mountain%20bought%20Access%20Technologies%2C%20along%20with%20SmarterDx%20and%20Thoughtful%20AI%2C%20to%20build%20its%20own%20competitor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224384%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22R1%20RCM%20logo%20on%20a%20smartphone%20screen.%20R1%20RCM%20was%20bought%20by%20TowerBrook%20and%20CD%26amp%3BR%20last%20year.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F684b2ee3f748d8c055f39932%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223288%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETowerBrook%20and%20CD%26amp%3BR%20last%20year%20bought%20R1%20RCM%20for%20%248.9%20billion%20last%20year%20after%20New%20Mountain's%20bid.%3Cp%3EIllustration%20by%20Piotr%20Swat%2FSOPA%20Images%2FLightRocket%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20private%20equity's%20rocky%20track%20record%20in%20healthcare%20looms.%20The%20industry%20has%20frequently%20faced%20criticisms%20that%20its%20cost-cutting%20priorities%2C%20when%20applied%20to%20healthcare%2C%20can%20put%20patient%20health%20at%20risk.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerican-hospitals-bankrupt-closing-wealthy-investors-looting-reselling-private-equity-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESteward%20Health%20Care%3C%2Fa%3E%20even%20drew%20a%20congressional%20inquiry%20into%20its%20operations%20last%20year%20after%20the%20hospital%20system%20formerly%20owned%20by%20a%20PE%20firm%20declared%20bankruptcy%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20return%20potentials%20in%20healthtech%20VC%20don't%20look%20as%20attractive%20as%20they%20did%20in%202021%20at%20digital%20health's%20fundraising%20peak.%20The%20first%20digital%20health%20company%20to%20IPO%20this%20year%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finvestors-executives-got-rich-hinge-health-ipo-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EHinge%20Health%2C%20went%20public%20at%20a%20%242.6%20billion%20valuation%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20last%20being%20privately%20valued%20at%20%246.2%20billion%20in%202021.%20The%20second%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fheres-who-got-rich-omada-healths-ipo-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EOmada%20Health%2C%20went%20public%20at%20a%20%241.1%20billion%3C%2Fa%3E%20valuation%2C%20roughly%20flat%20with%20its%20last%20private%20valuation%20of%20over%20%241%20billion%2C%20notched%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHolt%20said%20New%20Mountain's%20ability%20to%20combine%20PE%20and%20VC%20sensibilities%2C%20its%20focus%20on%20technology%2C%20and%20its%20close%20collaboration%20with%20founders%20have%20helped%20the%20firm%20gain%20ground%20in%20healthcare%2C%20where%20other%20investors%20have%20misstepped.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20a%20number%20of%20PE%20firms%20that%20don't%20really%20know%20how%20to%20maintain%20a%20growth-oriented%20culture%20with%20a%20founder-led%20business%2C%26quot%3B%20Holt%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20make%20a%20point%20to%20treat%20everyone%20well%20and%20execute%20what%20we%20say%20we're%20going%20to%20execute.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHolt%20estimates%20he's%20built%20close%20relationships%20with%2050-plus%20healthcare%20founders%20and%20executives%2C%20a%20talent%20bench%20he's%20repeatedly%20drawn%20on%20when%20launching%20new%20ventures.%20Datavant's%20Armbrester%2C%20who%20Holt%20previously%20brought%20on%20as%20the%20CEO%20of%20Signify%20Health%2C%20said%20Holt%20has%20notched%20partnerships%2C%20co-invested%20with%2C%20or%20forged%20relationships%20with%20every%20major%20health%20insurer%2C%20hospital%20system%2C%20and%20pharma%20company.%20He%20doesn't%20cold-call%20founders%3B%20he%20already%20knows%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20the%20guy%20has%20ever%20had%20a%20meal%20alone%2C%26quot%3B%20Armbrester%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20New%20Mountain%20sees%20so%20much%20opportunity%20in%20new%20healthcare%20AI%20applications%2C%20like%20using%20AI%20to%20manage%20hospital%20billing%20and%20claims%2C%20that%20it's%20less%20concerned%20with%20the%20recent%20exit%20drought%2C%20said%20Jeremy%20Delinsky%2C%20the%20new%20CEO%20of%20Smarter%20Technologies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20working%20in%20a%20very%20narrow%20use%20case%20where%20the%20return%20on%20investment%20isn't%20as%20clear%20cut%2C%20you're%20worried%20about%2C%20are%20you%20buying%20an%20asset%20at%20the%20point%20where%20it's%20worth%20the%20most%3F%26quot%3B%20Delinsky%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20%5Brevenue%20cycle%5D%20might%20be%20one%20of%20the%20single%20biggest%20and%20b