0San%20Francisco.%20There%2C%20I%20met%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetlify-jamstack-raises-53-million-2020-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ENetlify%3C%2Fa%3E%20CEO%20Mathias%20Biilmann%20and%20the%20startup's%20security%20chief%20Mark%20Dorsi.%20They%20showed%20me%20a%20live%20Slack%20feed%20where%20new%20apps%20were%20being%20deployed%20on%20Netlify's%20platform%2C%20roughly%20one%20every%2010%20seconds.%20Many%20of%20these%20were%20created%20using%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstackblitz-bolt-silicon-valley-hottest-ai-coding-startup-nearly-died-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBolt%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20similar%20AI%20coding%20services.%20And%20most%20were%20internal%20tools%20built%20by%20companies%20for%20their%20own%20use.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20a%20sea%20change.%20Historically%2C%20the%20decision%20to%20buy%20SaaS%20products%20stemmed%20from%20the%20high%20cost%20and%20complexity%20of%20building%20software%20internally.%20Skilled%20developers%20are%20expensive%20and%20internal%20IT%20teams%20are%20often%20stretched%20thin.%20But%20with%20AI-assisted%20software%20development%2C%20the%20economics%20shift.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETools%20like%20Bolt%20empower%20a%20new%20class%20of%20developer%20%E2%80%94%20what%20Biilmann%20calls%20%26quot%3BAI-native%20developers%26quot%3B%20and%20what%20Bolt%20calls%20%26quot%3Bsoftware%20composers.%26quot%3B%20These%20are%20non-traditional%20developers%2C%20often%20from%20business%20or%20operations%20roles%2C%20who%20can%20now%20build%20apps%20using%20AI%20to%20generate%20functional%20code%20through%20English%20language%20prompts.%20Training%20these%20new%20builders%20takes%20weeks%20or%20months%2C%20not%20years%20of%20expensive%20computer-science%20study.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%2C%20there%20will%20likely%20be%20a%20huge%20influx%20of%20new%20developers.%20This%20new%20supply%20means%20businesses%20can%20hire%20more%20coders%20for%20less%20money.%20That%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20will%20help%20companies%20tackle%20software%20projects%20that%20previously%20wouldn't%20have%20made%20the%20cut.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20where%20the%20build-versus-buy%20equation%20starts%20changing%2C%26quot%3B%20Biilmann%20told%20me.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20have%20millions%20of%20new%20people%20who%20can%20build%20software%2C%20the%20barrier%20goes%20down.%20What%20a%20single%20internal%20developer%20can%20build%20inside%20a%20company%20increases%20dramatically.%20It's%20a%20much%20more%20radical%20change%20to%20the%20whole%20ecosystem%20than%20people%20think.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a9e546c5-24f7-4b16-abde-e20a5d404589%5C%22%3EWhere%20this%20shift%20will%20happen%20first%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20than%2010%2C000%20new%20websites%20are%20being%20created%20via%20new%20AI%20coding%20tools%20and%20launched%20each%20day%20on%20Netlify's%20platform%20(versus%20being%20coded%20only%20by%20human%20developers)%2C%20he%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBiilman%20sees%20the%20build-versus-buy%20shift%20happening%20in%20these%20software%20areas%20first%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EHR%2C%20Training%2C%20Q%26amp%3BA%3A%20These%20are%20often%20pretty%20simple%20applications%20that%20read%20and%20write%20data%20and%20do%20visualizations.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ERevenue%20Operations%2C%20CPQ%2C%20Business%20Dashboards%3A%20AI%20coding%20tools%20and%20agents%20can%20easily%20build%20interfaces%20or%20visualizations%20on%20top%20of%20existing%20company%20data.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMarketing%20tools%3A%20These%20are%20relatively%20simple%20from%20a%20software%20perspective%20and%20they%20often%20need%20to%20be%20highly%20customized%20to%20specific%20company%20needs.%20What%20if%20AI%20agents%20write%20these%20applications%3F%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20so%20many%20other%20areas%20that%20will%20be%20impacted%20by%20this%2C%20that%20it's%20daunting%20to%20think%20through%20the%20full%20implications%2C%26quot%3B%20Biilmann%20added.%20%26quot%3BBut%20these%20are%20some%20of%20the%20easy%2C%20low-hanging%20areas.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226f95a1fb-3751-4a51-8697-de2c07c72346%5C%22%3EWho's%20building%20what%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENetlify%20used%20AI%20coding%20tools%20to%20build%20an%20internal%20employee%20survey%20tool%2C%20a%20task%20typically%20outsourced%20to%20SaaS%20providers%20such%20as%20Qualtrics%20or%20Momentive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20example%3A%20a%20revenue%20operations%20staffer%20at%20Netlify%20used%20Bolt%20to%20create%20a%20pricing%20calculator%20for%20enterprise%20deals%2C%20potentially%20replacing%20a%20category%20of%20SaaS%20known%20as%20CPQ%20(Configure%2C%20Price%2C%20Quote)%20software.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20a%20Netlify%20recruiter%20built%20a%20new%20in-house%20Interview%20Training%20Course%20app%20for%20hiring%20managers%20with%20an%20AI%20coding%20tool%20called%20Lovable%2C%20instead%20of%20buying%20from%20an%20external%20provider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20VCs%20are%20embracing%20this%20trend%20by%20actually%20doing%20some%20of%20the%20work%20themselves.%20Martin%20Casado%2C%20a%20general%20partner%20at%20Andreessen%20Horowitz%2C%20recently%20built%20his%20own%20AI-powered%20customer-relationship-management%20tool.%20CRM%20software%20is%20the%20core%20offering%20of%20tech%20giant%20Salesforce.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20some%20software%2C%20it's%20becoming%20quicker%20to%20code%20my%20own%20version%20with%20AI%20than%20learn%20someone%20else's%20non-intuitive%2C%20shit%20UI%2C%26quot%3B%20Casado%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fmartin_casado%2Fstatus%2F1927455230901227814%3Fs%3D46%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewrote%20on%20X%3C%2Fa%3E%20recently.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECasado's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fmartin_casado%2Fstatus%2F1927751400886337617%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECRM%20tool%3C%2Fa%3E%20syncs%20with%20his%20calendar%20and%20email%20accounts.%20It%20takes%20that%20information%20and%20queries%20AI%20models%20to%20plan%20out%20each%20week%2C%20researching%20the%20people%20and%20companies%20he's%20due%20to%20meet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226c49e59d-3252-4046-86e9-601baf3a3f80%5C%22%3EA%20note%20of%20caution%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fconsulting-firm-rips-up-traditional-billing-playbook-ai-era-globant-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMart%C3%ADn%20Migoya%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20CEO%20of%20tech%20consulting%20firm%20Globant%2C%20has%20spotted%20this%20trend.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20seeing%20projects%20that%20are%20coming%20out%20that%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20a%20recent%20interview%2C%20noting%20that%20some%20companies%20are%20beginning%20to%20try%20to%20replace%20unsatisfactory%20software%20services%20with%20internally-built%20alternatives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20he%20urged%20caution.%20%26quot%3BCreating%20enterprise-class%20things%20is%20tough%2C%26quot%3B%20Migoya%20added.%20AI%20models%20are%20improving%2C%20but%20software%20will%20still%20require%20support%2C%20the%20CEO%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20view%20reflects%20a%20common%20concern%3A%20maintenance%20and%20reliability.%20If%20something%20breaks%20in%20an%20AI-coded%20internal%20app%2C%20who%20fixes%20it%3F%20This%20is%20where%20infrastructure%20plays%20a%20critical%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20address%20these%20concerns%2C%20companies%20like%20Netlify%20are%20developing%20what%20Biilmann%20calls%20%26quot%3Bopinionated%20platforms%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20infrastructure%20stacks%20optimized%20for%20AI-generated%20code%20and%20agents.%20These%20platforms%20handle%20authentication%2C%20authorization%2C%20staging%2C%20security%2C%20and%20data%20access%20in%20standardized%20ways%2C%20reducing%20the%20operational%20burden.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20evolution%20could%20enable%20companies%20to%20move%20from%20building%20prototypes%20to%20deploying%20production-grade%20software%2C%20without%20hiring%20an%20army%20of%20senior%20support%20engineers%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d2a66246-904b-44d7-8d69-b3ef610381df%5C%22%3EThe%20strategic%20implications%20for%20SaaS%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20implications%20for%20the%20SaaS%20industry%20are%20significant.%20If%20companies%20can%20build%20tailored%20internal%20tools%20for%20the%20same%20cost%2C%20or%20less%2C%20than%20SaaS%20subscriptions%2C%20the%20traditional%20SaaS%20model%20could%20be%20under%20threat.%20Per-seat%20pricing%20may%20start%20to%20look%20expensive%20when%20compared%20to%20more%20abundant%20AI-assisted%2C%20in-house%20human%20coders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESalesforce%2C%20the%20standard%20bearer%20of%20SaaS%2C%20could%20be%20vulnerable.%20While%20their%20core%20CRM%20system%20of%20record%20may%20remain%20sticky%2C%20some%20of%20the%20custom%20functionality%20layered%20on%20top%20might%20be%20replicated%20with%20AI-coding%20tools.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSalesforce%20is%20really%20afraid%2C%26quot%3B%20Biilmann%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20are%20not%20going%20to%20be%20vibe%20coded%20away%20from%20being%20the%20system%20of%20record%20for%20all%20your%20sales%20data.%20But%20it's%20much%20more%20likely%20that%20a%20lot%20of%20their%20own%20custom%20functionality%20on%20top%20of%20that%2C%20that%20they%20charge%20extra%20for%20today%2C%20gets%20replaced%20by%20people%20building%20their%20own%20custom%20functionality.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESalesforce's%20answer%2C%20so%20far%2C%20is%20to%20build%20and%20launch%20its%20own%20array%20of%20AI%20agents.%20This%20Agentforce%20business%20is%20showing%20early%20signs%20of%20traction%20with%20customers%2C%20so%20this%20company%20may%20be%20well%20placed%20to%20fend%20off%20the%20threat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOthers%20may%20not%20be%20so%20lucky.%20Consulting%20firm%20AlixPartners%20recently%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsoftware-companies-squeezed-by-ai-alixpartners-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewarned%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20more%20than%20100%20midmarket%20software%20companies%20are%20stuck%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20this%20disruptive%20AI%20trend.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221a184ac1-e734-4dcc-bde2-d4e6c4da7183%5C%22%3EA%20massive%20new%20software%20layer%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20new%20wave%20of%20software%20probably%20won't%20replace%20systems%20of%20record%2C%20it%20will%20sit%20on%20top%20of%20them.%20Think%20internal%20dashboards%2C%20pricing%20calculators%2C%20contract%20tools%2C%20HR%20survey%20apps%2C%20and%20media%20monitoring%20systems.%20All%20these%20are%20traditionally%20handled%20by%20SaaS%20vendors.%20But%20as%20internal%20developers%20gain%20new%20AI%20superpowers%2C%20building%20these%20tools%20in-house%20becomes%20a%20viable%20option.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI-assisted%20software%20development%20is%20tipping%20the%20scales%20in%20the%20build-versus-buy%20debate.%20While%20it%20won't%20kill%20off%20the%20SaaS%20industry%20overnight%2C%20it%20introduces%20a%20powerful%20alternative.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECompanies%20that%20embrace%20this%20model%20may%20be%20able%20to%20gain%20more%20control%2C%20reduce%20costs%2C%20and%20innovate%20faster.%20Those%20that%20cling%20solely%20to%20traditional%20SaaS%20may%20find%20themselves%20paying%20more%20for%20less%2C%20while%20their%20competitors%20build%20the%20future%20from%20within.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can%20now%20become%20a%20software%20developer%20without%20writing%20code%2C%26quot%3B%20Biilmann%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20going%20to%20have%20a%20ripple%20effect%20on%20everything%20that's%20been%20built.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3ESign%20up%20for%20BI's%20Tech%20Memo%20newsletter%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsubscription%2Fnewsletter%2Ftech-memo%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Ehere%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E.%20Reach%20out%20