3Cp%3EConsistency%20means%20building%20an%20everyday%20relationship%20with%20AI%20%E2%80%94%20and%20that%20starts%20small%2C%20said%20Gridley.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20has%20to%20start%20super%20easy.%20You%20have%20to%20give%20them%20things%20that%20take%20no%20more%20than%20a%20minute%20or%20two%20to%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20help%20her%20team%20form%20the%20habit%2C%20she%20created%20%26quot%3B30%20Days%20of%20GPT%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20a%20list%20of%20daily%20micro-tasks%20designed%20to%20ingrain%20AI%20use.%20The%20list%20begins%20with%20simple%20prompts%2C%20like%20uploading%20your%20calendar%20into%20ChatGPT%20and%20asking%20for%20meeting%20talking%20points.%20It%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eeventually%20moves%20into%20more%20complex%20tasks%20like%20%26quot%3Breverse-engineer%20prompts%20to%20make%20LLMs%20think%20like%20you.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGrindley%20said%20she%20avoids%20frontloading%20real%2C%20complex%20work%20into%20the%20process.%20She's%20focused%20on%20forming%20habits%2C%20not%20on%20education.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWork%20is%20hard%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20start%20with%20things%20that%20are%20just%20fun%2C%20simple%20use%20cases.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20know%20anyone%20who%20has%20gone%20through%20this%20and%20not%20come%20out%20the%20other%20side%20feeling%20a%20hundred%20times%20more%20confident%20in%20their%20skills%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221d3b2e57-4274-4615-ace8-2a2219935644%5C%22%3ECreate%20a%20reward%20loop%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20key%20to%20her%20strategy%20is%20designing%20a%20reward%20loop%20%E2%80%94%20a%20crucial%20but%20often%20overlooked%20part%20of%20behavior%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20needs%20to%20be%20powerful%2C%20immediate%2C%20and%20emotional%2C%20Gridley%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20this%20person%20does%20the%20thing%20that%20you%20want%20them%20to%20do%2C%20they%20feel%20like%20a%20million%20bucks%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20way%20she%20makes%20that%20happen%20is%20through%20Custom%20GPTs.%20Team%20members%20can%20upload%20a%20document%20and%20get%20immediate%20feedback%20or%20an%20improved%20version%20%E2%80%94%20no%20advanced%20prompting%20needed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20get%20the%20joy%20of%2C%20'Oh%2C%20this%20helps%20me%2C%20this%20was%20cool'%20without%20any%20of%20the%20despair%20of%2C%20'Oh%2C%20I'm%20not%20very%20good%20at%20prompting%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGridley%20also%20said%20giving%20shout-outs%20in%20team%20meetings%20and%20encouraging%20demos%20when%20someone%20uses%20AI%20to%20solve%20a%20real%20problem%20are%20effective%20ways%20to%20recognize%20and%20reward%20adoption.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20I'm%20trying%20to%20build%20any%20kind%20of%20habit%20on%20my%20team%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bit's%20less%20about%20the%20accountability%20of%20how%20I'm%20enforcing%20this%2C%20and%20more%20about%20how%20I%20make%20it%20so%20rewarding%20for%20people%20to%20do%20it%20that%20they%20do%20it%20naturally.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGridley%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHer%20comments%20come%20as%20the%20corporate%20rush%20to%20adopt%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-leaders-pwc-mastercard-accenture-ikea-tech-adoption-growth-strategy-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI%20is%20shifting%20into%20high%20gear%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20three-quarters%20of%20business%20people%20surveyed%20by%20McKinsey%20said%20their%20companies%20used%20AI%20for%20at%20least%20one%20business%20task%20as%20of%20July%202024%2C%20up%20from%2055%25%20since%20late%202023%2C%20according%20to%20a%20March%20report.%20The%20consultancy%20surveyed%20nearly%201%2C500%20participants%20online%20across%20various%20industries%2C%20company%20sizes%2C%20tenures%2C%20and%20regions%2C%20inclu