g%20the%20waters%2C%20hoping%20to%20create%20a%20space%20where%20anyone%20could%20walk%20in%2C%20pick%20up%20a%20drum%2C%20and%20feel%20part%20of%20something.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20within%20a%20short%20time%2C%20officials%20came%20over%20and%20asked%20them%20to%20stop.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20asked%20us%20to%20stop%20whatever%20we%20were%20doing%20because%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20court%20and%20there%20was%20some%20examination%20going%20on%2C%E2%80%9D%20Gaurav%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-13T181144.051_11zon-1749819081.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22people%20at%20BDC%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-13T181144.051_11zon-1749819081.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-13T181144.051_11zon-1749819081-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-13T181144.051_11zon-1749819081-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-13T181144.051_11zon-1749819081-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-13T181144.051_11zon-1749819081-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-449011%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EWhile%20the%20idea%20was%20great%2C%20Gaurav%20had%20to%20figure%20how%20this%20can%20be%20implemented%20in%20Bengaluru.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20small%20disruption%20was%20enough%20to%20make%20him%20realise%20that%20Bengaluru%20wouldn%