Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20others%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20simply%20a%20refreshing%20change%20from%20the%20usual.%20%3Cstrong%3EAbhijith%20Ravi%20Kumar%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20a%20general%20manager%20and%20musician%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20personally%20liked%20BDC%20because%20I%20got%20to%20explore%20rhythm%20beyond%20the%20tabla%20I%20play.%20Even%20my%20small%20daughter%20had%20a%20good%20time%20in%20the%20session.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20makes%20Gaurav%20happiest%20is%20seeing%20how%20naturally%20people%20of%20all%20ages%20and%20backgrounds%20show%20up.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20fathers%20coming%20with%20their%20daughters.%20We%20have%20husbands%20and%20wives.%20We%20have%20people%20who%20are%20dating%20each%20other.%20We%20have%20kids%20coming%20over.%20We%20have%20a%20bunch%20of%20only%20ladies%20coming%20over%20at%20different%20ages.%20It%E2%80%99s%20beautiful%20to%20see%20how%20percussion%20unites%20people%20despite%20the%20differences%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ERun%20by%20volunteers%2C%20driven%20by%20passion%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20its%20core%2C%20BDC%20remains%20a%20passion%20project%20%E2%80%94%20built%20entirely%20on%20voluntary%20effort%20and%20the%20love%20for%20rhythm.%20While%20Gaurav%20and%20his%20two%20co-founders%20handle%20most%20of%20the%20key%20decisions%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20the%20small%20team%20of%20volunteers%20that%20keeps%20everything%20running%20%E2%80%94%20from%20securing%20venues%2C%20managing%20logistics%2C%20handling%20registrations%2C%20to%20managing%20the%20online%20presence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20cover%20basic%20expenses%2C%20they%20charge%20a%20small%20registration%20fee%20of%20%E2%82%B9200%20for%20each%20session.%20Whatever%20comes%20in%20gets%20reinvested%20to%20make%20the%20experience%20better%20for%20everyone%20who%20attends.%20The%20team%20also%20follows%20a%20three-week%20cycle%2C%20giving%20themselves%20enough%20breathing%20space%20between%20events%20to%20plan%20and%20rese