Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERunning%20BDC%20alongside%20his%20corporate%20job%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20been%20easy%20for%20Gaurav.%20The%20weekdays%20are%20packed%20with%20work%20at%20Infosys%2C%20and%20most%20of%20the%20organising%20happens%20over%20weekends.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIs%20it%20difficult%3F%20Absolutely!%20Monday%20to%20Friday%20is%20crazy.%20I%20take%20Saturdays%20and%20Sundays%20to%20manage%20this%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20for%20him%2C%20BDC%20isn%E2%80%99t%20just%20a%20side%20hobby%20%E2%80%94%20it%E2%80%99s%20something%20that%20gives%20him%20balance%20and%20joy%2C%20even%20with%20a%20packed%20schedule.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Chaithra%20puts%20it%2C%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20tend%20to%20think%20that%20being%20in%20corporate%20and%20having%20an%20artistic%20lens%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20go%20hand-in-hand.%20But%20this%20drums%20circle%20has%20proved%20that%20wrong%20since%20I%20have%20seen%20people%20from%20different%20and%20diverse%20professions%20attending%20joyfully.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELooking%20ahead%2C%20Gaurav%20hopes%20BDC%20will%20continue%20to%20grow%20into%20something%20more%20%E2%80%94%20a%20platform%20that%20gives%20both%20musicians%20and%20non-musicians%20a%20chance%20to%20experience%20rhythm%20in%20its%20purest%20form.%20The%20team%20is%20also%20planning%20to%20start%20a%20podcast%20called%20%3Cstrong%3EAmongst%20Us%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20where%20they%20will%20share%20stories%20of%20regular%20people%20who%E2%80%99ve%20found%20joy%2C%20connection%2C%20and%20friendship%20through%20percussion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBDC%20started%20with%20one%20person%20looking%20for%20company.%20Today%2C%20it%20has%20become%20a%20reminder%20that%20sometimes%2C%20even%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20a%20busy%20city%2C%20people%20will%20always%20find%20ways%20to%20come%20together.%20As%20long%20as%20someone%20is%20willing%20to%20take%20the%20first%20step.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Khushi%20Arora%3B%20All%20images%20courtesy%20BDC.%3C%2F